data.description: Welcome to 3324 Reedy Glen Dr. in the beautiful city of Kissimmee, FL! This stunning home offers an array of desirable features that are sure to impress even the most discerning buyers. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the elegant tile flooring that spans throughout the main living areas, providing a sleek and modern aesthetic. The high ceilings add a sense of grandeur and create an open and airy atmosphere, complemented by an abundance of natural light that floods the space.    The heart of this home is the pristine bright kitchen, a chef's dream come true. It boasts ample cabinetry, providing plenty of storage space, and offers a clean and timeless look. The kitchen serves as a focal point for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals. This amazing single-family home, built in 2018, features a spacious and open floor plan with the kitchen overlooking the living room and dining room. Ceramic tile flooring graces the common areas and bedrooms.    What makes this home even more remarkable is the addition of solar panels, contributing to energy efficiency and cost savings. This property enjoys an excellent location, in close proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment, with easy access to major roads such as I-4, US 17-92, S John Young Pkwy, and Poinciana Blvd. Plus, it's less than 20 miles away from Orlando International Airport, Universal Studios, and Disney World. Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautiful and energy-efficient home in a prime location!
